{"tid":2062745,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九西馮達浚：一我可殺，而繼我而起者不可盡殺","createTime":"2020-06-13T10:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T09:59:11.000Z","uid":200122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"82285e646e7c75ecfff30843b59acff221385d2b","tid":2062745,"uid":200122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frankiefung.hk/photos/a.436948740167745/846276765901605/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrankiefung.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.436948740167745%2F846276765901605%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJroOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=1bae2728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frankiefung.hk/photos/a.436948740167745/846276765901605/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n連結香港共同體的不只是痛苦，還有對<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港的盼望。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一年以來，政權靠著暴力，營造恐懼、驚慌的氛圍，意圖恫嚇反對聲音。警棍、子彈殘害肉體之餘，廣大群眾更蒙受極大心理傷害，抗爭者的精神不知不覺間被政權的一舉一動牽引著，無力感、麻木、內疚等情緒接踵而來。<br />\n<br />\n然而政權的暴力永遠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不能撲熄人民的意志</span></strong>，它反而成為了香港人連結的參考點，造就了香港共同體的形成。警暴讓不少本來不熱衷政治的人，開始關懷公共事務、參與公民社會。警暴讓我們發掘了同行兒女之間「打在你身痛在我心」的切膚之痛，驅使我們互相扶持，在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港的路途上堅強走下去</span></strong>。同理心讓我們分清敵我，為「香港人」的定義加添了一層情感上的內涵。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚舉辦的612遍地開花展覽，就是希望提醒我們一路走來的心路歷程，這些情感將是抗爭的動員能力基礎。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">極權總是懼怕群眾的力量</span></strong>，警方昨日在展區濫捕，就是想窒礙共同體彼此情感上的連結。<br />\n<br />\n極權越想擊散我們，我們就越要時刻銘記對共同體的忠誠和歸屬。當我們視<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港的前途為共業</span></strong>，將有不計其數的同伴投身革命&mdash;&mdash;「一<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[black]<span style=\"color: red;\">我可殺，而繼我而起者不可盡殺</span>[/black]</span></strong>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsBTysi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsBTysi.jpg&h=74ce8d0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3159131a76c7982c2194cce56025f7c690412f6","tid":2062745,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"共同體同民族有無分別？"},{"pid":"65a7ecca40aacf19d7108b389bf9660cb2b9bfb4","tid":2062745,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3159131a76c7982c2194cce56025f7c690412f6","tid":2062745,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"共同體同民族有無分別？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"共同體可以唔係民族，民族一定係共同體<br />\n香港人係咪一定係民族，唔肯定<br />\n但我地一定係共存亡嘅一群人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14c5214b357fa55687dcaae7d94312849a4ee87","tid":2062745,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65a7ecca40aacf19d7108b389bf9660cb2b9bfb4","tid":2062745,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3159131a76c7982c2194cce56025f7c690412f6","tid":2062745,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"共同體同民族有無分別？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"共同體可以唔係民族，民族一定係共同體<br />\n香港人係咪一定係民族，唔肯定<br />\n但我地一定係共存亡嘅一群人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"咁似乎其實都係一個相近嘅concept<br />\n都係偏本士"},{"pid":"0f45f47f7aa417f9b39639c66d061fe502ccac5b","tid":2062745,"uid":200122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb9bbbb5763fa0b048476acea5f10fd17fc2b52","tid":2062745,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}